text: Escuela Integral de San Pablo Tacachico are a Salvadoran professional football club based in San Pablo Tacachico, La Libertad, El Salvador. The club currently plays in the Segunda División de Fútbol Salvadoreño. ==History== On the 2014 the club participe in the thirty division On 5 July 2015 the club had purchased a license to be able to compete in the newly increased second division. ==Honours== ===Domestic honours=== * Segunda División Salvadorean and predecessors * Champions (1) : Clausura 2019 * Tercera División Salvadorean and predecessors ** Champions:(1) : ==Personnel== ===Current technical staff=== {| |- | Head Coach | Efrain Burgos |- | Assistant coach | Juan Francisco Najarro |- | Medic | Dr Josean Garcia |- | Kinesology | Luisa Alas |- | Utility | Hector Avelar |- |} ==Current squad== As of Apertura 2018: ===Squad changes for the Apertura 2018=== In: * TBD – Transferred from Free Agent * TBD – Transferred from Free Agent Out: * TBA – Transferred to TBA ==List of coaches== * Angel Orellana (May 2015 – June 2015) * Efrain Burgos (June 2015 – Sep 2015) * Pablo Quiñonez (Sep 2015 – Dec 2015) * Miguel Angel Soriano (Dec 2015 – Feb 2016) * Juan Francisco Najarro (Mar 2016– Aug 2016) * Bairon Ernesto Garcia (Sep 2016–) * Juan Ramon Paredes (2016) * Pablo Quiñones (- June 2018) * Juan Ramon Sanchez (June 2018– July 2019) * Oscar 'Lagarto' Ulloa (July 2019-) ==References== ==External links== * http://www.ceroacero.es/equipa.php?id=67508 Category:Football clubs in El Salvador Category:Association football clubs established in 2015 Category:2015 establishments in El Salvador
